@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@authToken = {{login.response.body.token}}

### 1. 測試 API 是否存活 (Root)
GET http://localhost:5000/

### 2. 使用者註冊 (Register)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "New User",
    "email": "newuser@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### 3. 使用者登入 (Login) - 取得 Token
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@example.com",
    "password": "admin"
}

### 4. 取得我的資訊 (Get Me) - 需 Token
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 5. 取得所有貼文 (Get All Posts)
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts

### 6. 新增貼文 (Create Post) - 需 Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "測試貼文",
    "imageUrl": "https://www.toy-people.com/?p=49591",
    "category": "其他",
    "description": "這是透過 test.http 發送的測試貼文"
}

### 7. 刪除貼文 (需替換 ID)
# 請將 :id 替換為實際的 Post ID
# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/posts/:id
# Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
